  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine softened taleggio cheese, nuka-pickle, oats, salt, and black pepper. Mix well until combined.",
    "Add minced garlic to the cheese mixture and mix until well combined.",
    "Add chopped cilantro to the cheese mixture and mix until well combined.",
    "Transfer the cheese mixture to a baking dish and drizzle with balsamic vinegar.",
    "Drizzle the coconut oil over the cheese mixture and mix until well combined.",
    "Bake in preheated oven for 30 minutes or until the top is golden brown and the edges are crispy.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool for 10 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve warm, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
  ],
